<p>I just have a couple of questions. The first one was, &quot;Do I want to search?&quot; So, what I mean by that is a lot of the beautifulness about cities is about discovering the things yourself, about going out and being the browser. It feels like the functional need would be the search ability to be able to search data but that ability discovers what being innocent is about. The second question&hellip;</p>
